---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 542
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=The Oratory of the Heart
  - 944
By: Marsilio Ficino
---
Seek yourself outside of the world, but in order to seek and to find
yourself outside, fly outside, or rather look outside. ... Leave
behind the narrowness of this shadow and look within yourself.
